{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-page-jsx","path":"/blog/jekyll-setup-xubuntu","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Installing Jekyll on Xubuntu","date":"2015-05-19","description":null,"tags":["jekyll","xubuntu","setup"]},"html":"<p><a href=\"http://jekyllrb.com/\">Jekyll</a> is a brilliant tool for static website creation, and installing its latest version on my Xubuntu 15 machine was definitely easy:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>Open a root shell by running:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> -i</code></pre></div>\n<p>and typing your password</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Execute:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">apt-get</span> <span class=\"token function\">install</span> ruby ruby-dev nodejs</code></pre></div>\n<p>and confirm</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Run:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">gem <span class=\"token function\">install</span> jekyll</code></pre></div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Exit the root shell:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token builtin class-name\">exit</span></code></pre></div>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<p>And that's all! ^__^! Jekyll is now ready!</p>\n<h2>Further references</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"http://jekyllrb.com/\">Jekyll website</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://daringfireball.net/projects/markdown/\">Markdown syntax</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://markdownlivepreview.com/\">Markdown live preview</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://validator.w3.org/\">W3C Markup Validation Service</a></li>\n</ul>"}},"pageContext":{"nodeId":"c8e95105-a5bd-5b94-8474-0a9df2e632d7"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3159585216","3567824559"]}